cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.CV, cs.SY 

This paper deals with optimizing the transmission of multi-view videos in a wireless network, which involves aspects of networking (cs.NI), multimedia (cs.MM), information theory (cs.IT), computer vision (cs.CV), and control systems (cs.SY). The paper specifically focuses on exploiting both natural multicast opportunities and view synthesis-enabled multicast opportunities, which further supports the likelihood of these categories.
